modName: Draconicrose - AlienSlofs Better Trolls for Automatic Variants
summary: An Av Package with AlienSlof\\\'s Better Trolls textures.
descriptionHtml:
Just a simple Av Package so you can add [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/32779]AlienSlof\'s Better Trolls [/url] to your game. Unfortunately, and I think this is an AV bug, the Uderfrykte isn\'t varying correctly. I will update when I can fix that.

[size=30]Installation[/size]
Make sure you have [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21377]Automatic Variants[/url] installed. Then, extract the .zip into [b]Data/SkyProc Patchers/Automatic Variants/AV Packages[/b]. Run Automatic Variants and generate a new patch. Enjoy!
author: Draconicrose
